      skos:note "Validation criteria before promoting to decision: (1) additive vs. incremental test predicts conversion reliably across 2-3 more the enterprise customer-shape conversations; (2) process sale closes without requiring case studies; (3) engagement shape replicates across different org sizes. Rejection criteria: 3+ the enterprise customer-shape prospects fail to convert via process sale within 90 days, OR 2+ expertise-distributor prospects convert at higher rates than the enterprise customer-shape." ;
      narr:aboutNode narr:Narrative_EnterpriseShapePrimaryFocus ;
      narr:hasConvictionLevel narr:Conviction_Stake ;
      narr:supports narr:Narrative_SellTheProcessPreCaseStudy .

    narr:Claim_SMBPivotReconciliationNeeded a narr:Claim ;
